=== Loading images from a plug-in
		
			The
			`ImageDescriptor`
			class has a static method to
			create an
			`ImageDescriptor`
			instance
			directly from a URL.
			`ImageDescriptor`
			is a light-weight representation of an
			`Image`
			. Via the
			`createImage()`
			you can create the
			`Image`
			instance.
		
		
